data.whatILove: Here is the one you have been waiting for! This full brick custom home sits on over two acres with lots of privacy and room for future pool. Much thought and detail entered into the construction of this house evidenced by the poured concrete foundation, built in fire sprinkler system, whole house sound system and attractive trim work. TWO gorgeous kitchens include custom cabinets with soft close hinges, granite counter tops and tile back splash. The main level has a grand foyer, stacked stone fireplace and large kitchen open to dining area. The main floor master bedroom boasts a trey ceiling, walk in closet with custom shelving and over-sized tile shower. Upper level includes huge bonus/media room, third bedroom and bath. The walk out basement offers second living quarters with a full kitchen, second master, recreation area and family room. Outdoor kitchen with pizza oven and large patio. Drought tolerant Zoysia grass and the list goes on.
